ord last modified</item></change><change n="meta.704"><date>2009-03-20</date><respStmt><name>IDP</name></respStmt><item>Crosswalked to EpiDoc XML</item></change></revisionDesc></teiHeader><text><body><head lang="en"><date>257BC</date>
<placeName cert="high">Philadelphia</placeName>
<xref evaluate="all" from="ROOT" n="sb;3;6787" targOrder="U" to="DITTO" type="reprint from">SB3,6787;PEdg81</xref></head><div lang="grc" part="N" type="edition"><div n="r,1" part="N" type="textpart"><ab part="N">

    <lb n="1"/><gap desc="vestiges" extent="unknown" reason="illegible" unit="character"/> <supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ἐξ Ἡ</supplied><unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ρα</unclear>-

    <lb n="2"/>κλείας ἐχρήσ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">α</unclear><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">μ</supplied>εν ποτη<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ρ</unclear>ίδια. καὶ νῦ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ν</unclear> δε, 

    <lb n="3"/>ἐπειδὴ ἐκεῖνος μέν ἐστιν ἐν φυλακῆι, τὰ δὲ 

    <lb n="4"/>ὑπάρχοντα αὐτοῦ ἐξαργυρίζεται, γεγρά-

    <lb n="5"/>φαμεν Ἀπολλωνίωι, <add place="supralinear">ἧς καί σοι τὸ <choice><corr>ἀντίγραφον</corr><sic>ταντιγραφον</sic></choice> ὑπογέγραπται.</add> καλῶς οὖν ποιήσεις 

    <lb n="6"/>ἐπισκεψάμενος μετ᾽ Ἀρτεμιδώρου τοῦ 

    <lb n="7"/>ἰατροῦ εἰ φαίνεται ἀποδοῦναι αὐτῶι 

    <lb n="8"/>τὸ ἐπιστόλιον ἢ ἐᾶν οἰμώζειν. ὅτι <choice><corr>μὲν</corr><sic>μεγ</sic></choice> 

    <lb n="9"/>γὰρ ἡμέτερά ἐστιν τὰ ἀργυρωμάτια 

    <lb n="10"/>τὰ ὑπογεγραμμένα, τοῦ μὲν ψυκτῆρος 

    <lb n="11"/>καὶ <subst><add place="inline">ψυκτηριδίου</add><del rend="corrected">ψυ<gap extent="1" reason="illegible" unit="character"/>τηριδιου</del></subst> καὶ ἑνὸς τῶν Ἀντιπα-

    <lb n="12"/>τριδίων καὶ παρὰ τῶι βασιλεῖ ἐστὶ γραφὴ 

    <lb n="13"/>ἐν τῆι παρ᾽ Ἱκε<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">σίο</supplied>υ ἐπιστολῆι καὶ ἐν τῶι 

    <lb n="14"/>ἐνπορίωι ἀπο<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">γ</unclear><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ρ</supplied><unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">α</unclear>φή, τῶν δὲ λοιπῶν 

    <lb n="15"/>παρ᾽ ἡμῖν τ<gap extent="1" reason="illegible" unit="character"/><gap extent="unknown" reason="lost" unit="character"/><unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">τι</unclear><gap extent="1" reason="illegible" unit="character"/>υγον ὑπάρχει. 

    <lb n="16"/>ἐὰν δὲ μὴ φαί<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ν</unclear><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">η</supplied><unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">τ</unclear>αι ὑμῖν ἀποδοῦναι, 

    <lb n="17"/>Δημητρίου γε <supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ἐπ</supplied>ιμελόμενοι χαρι<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ε</unclear>ῖσθέ 

    <lb n="18"/>μοι· νῦν μὲν γὰ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ρ</unclear> αὐτὸν πυνθανόμεθα 

    <lb n="19"/>ὀλιγωρεῖσθαι. 

    <lb n="20"/>ἔρρωσο. 

    <lb n="21"/>Ἀπολλωνίωι. Δημήτριος ὁ ἐν τῶι Προσω-

    <lb n="22"/>πίτηι ὑπὸ σοῦ κατασταθεὶς ἀντιγρα-

    <lb n="23"/>φεύς, διὰ τὸ ἐξ οἴκου τε ἀποδημεῖν 

    <lb n="24"/>οὐχ ὡς μενῶν καὶ ἔτι περικοπῆναι 

    <lb n="25"/>ὑπὸ Λυσιμάχου τοῦ <choice><corr>λῃστοῦ</corr><sic>ληιστου</sic></choice> τὸ με-

    <lb n="26"/><subst><add place="inline"><unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">θό</unclear>διον</add><del rend="corrected">με<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">σι</unclear>διον</del></subst> καὶ τὸν παῖδα, ὡς ὑπὸ σοῦ 

    <lb n="27"/>κατείχετο, ἠξίου <add place="supralinear">ἡμᾶς</add> <del rend="erasure">αυ</del> κερμάτιον αὐ-

    <lb n="28"/>τῶι προχρῆσαι, ἵνα κατασκευασθῆι 

    <lb n="29"/>τοῖς ἀναγκαίοις. ἀργύριον μὲν <unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ο</unclear><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ὖ</supplied>ν οὐκ εἴχομεν 

    <lb n="30"/>αὐτῶι προχρῆσαι, ποτηρίδια <add place="supralinear">δὲ</add> ἐ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">χρ</unclear>ήσαμεν 

    <lb n="31"/>ὧν σὺ Τρυφέραι ἔξ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ω</unclear>θεν συνέθη<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">κ</supplied>ας, ψυκτη-

    <lb n="32"/>ρίδιόν τε στατόν, <unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">μ</unclear><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ικ</supplied>ρῶι πλ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">έ</unclear><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ο</supplied><unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ν</unclear> <supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ἢ</supplied> <unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">χο</unclear>ῦν χώρουν, 

    <lb n="33"/>οὗ ὁλκὴ <unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ἐ</unclear><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">κ τ</supplied>ῆς πα<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ρ</unclear>᾽ <supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ἡμ</supplied><unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ῖν</unclear> γρ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">αφῆς</unclear> <gap extent="3" reason="illegible" unit="character"/> 

    <lb n="34"/>καὶ ψυκ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">τήριο</unclear>ν καὶ Ἀ<gap extent="6" reason="lost" unit="character"/><gap extent="3" reason="illegible" unit="character"/><gap extent="6" reason="lost" unit="character"/><gap extent="3" reason="illegible" unit="character"/> 
</ab></div><div n="r,2" part="N" type="textpart"><ab part="N">

    <lb n="34"/><gap extent="1" reason="illegible" unit="line"/> 

    <lb n="35"/>θαι. καλῶς <unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">δ</unclear>᾽ <unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ἂν</unclear> 

    <lb n="36"/>ποιοῖς <unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">καὶ</unclear> <unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">συγ</unclear>-

    <lb n="37"/>γνώμην ἡμῖν 

    <lb n="38"/>ἔχων· οὐ γὰρ ἂν 

    <lb n="39"/>ἠλπίσαμεν 

    <lb n="40"/>ἐν οὕτω βραχεῖ 

    <lb n="41"/>χρόνωι διαπε-

    <lb n="42"/>σεῖν αὐτόν. 

    <lb n="43"/>ἔρρωσο. 
</ab></div><div n="v" part="N" type="textpart"><ab part="N">

    <lb n="44"/><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">Ἀ</supplied><unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">μύντας</unclear> περὶ Δημητρίου. 

    <lb n="45"/><supplied cert="high" reason="lost"><expan><ex cert="high">ἔτους</ex></expan></supplied> <num value="28">κη</num> Περιτίου <num value="22">κβ</num>, 

    <lb n="46"/><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ἐν</supplied> Βουβάστωι. 

    <lb n="44"/>Ζήνωνι. </ab></div></div><div n="meta.704" part="N" type="description"><p><rs cert="high" type="material">Papyrus</rs></p></div><div n="meta.704" part="N" subtype="textDate" type="commentary"><p><date notAfter="-0257-03-26" type="textDate">vor 26. März 257 v.Chr.</date></p></div><div n="meta.704" part="N" subtype="mentionedDates" type="commentary"><head>Erwähnte Daten</head><p>verso Z. 2: <date type="mentioned" value="-0257-03-26">26. März 257 v.Chr.</date></p></div><div n="meta.704" part="N" subtype="principalEdition" type="bibliography"><listBibl><bibl subtype="principal" type="publication"><title level="s" type="abbreviated">P.Cair. Zen.</title><biblScope type="volume">1</biblScope><biblScope type="numbers">59044</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="Trismegistos"><biblScope type="numbers">704</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="DDbDP"><series>0092</series>; <biblScope type="volume">1</biblScope>; <biblScope type="numbers">59044</biblScope></bibl></listBibl><p>Perseus links: <xref evaluate="all" from="ROOT" href="0092;1;59044" targOrder="Y" to="DITTO" type="Perseus">Text in Perseus</xref></p></div><div n="meta.704" part="N" subtype="corrections" type="bibliography"><head>BL-Einträge nach BL-Konkordanz</head><listBibl><bibl type="BL"><biblScope type="volume">IX</biblScope>, S. <biblScope type="pages">49</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="BL"><biblScope type="volume">XI</biblScope>, S. <biblScope type="pages">54</biblScope></bibl></listBibl></div><div n="meta.704" part="N" subtype="illustrations" type="bibliography"><p><bibl type="illustration">Pl. XIV</bibl><bibl type="illustration">Seider, Paläographie III, 1, II Abb. 39 (Rekto, Z. 1-20 und 35-43), S. 211 und II Abb. 39 a, S. 213</bibl><bibl type="illustration">Crisci, Scrivere greco, Tav. VI</bibl></p></div><div n="meta.704" part="N" subtype="otherPublications" type="bibliography"><head>Andere Publikationen</head><listBibl><bibl subtype="other" type="publication">SB III 6787</bibl><bibl subtype="other" type="publication">C.Ptol.Sklav. II 224</bibl><bibl subtype="other" type="publication">C.Zen.Palestine 52</bibl></listBibl></div><div n="meta.704" part="N" subtype="translations" type="bibliography"><head>Übersetzungen</head><listBibl lang="en"><head lang="de">Englisch:</head><bibl type="translations">C.C. Edgar, ASAE 23, 1923, S. 195-196.</bibl></listBibl><listBibl lang="fr"><head lang="de">Französisch:</head><bibl type="translations">Orrieux, Les papyrus de Zenon (1983), S. 69-70</bibl></listBibl></div><div n="meta.704" part="N" subtype="locations" type="history"><p><placeName cert="high" type="ancientFindspot">Alexandria</placeName></p></div><div n="meta.704" part="N" type="figure"><p><figure href="http://ipap.csad.ox.ac.uk/4DLink4/4DACTION/IPAPwebquery?vPub=P.Cair.Zen.&amp;vVol=1&amp;vNum=59044"><figDesc>Abbildung im Internet</figDesc></figure></p></div></body></text></TEI.2>